# Library/validation reports are deterministic generator/validator outputs.
# Regenerate locally as needed (see docs/ai-kb/09_validation_checklist.md);
# they are not committed baseline fixtures. The two !-prefixed files below
# are hand-curated inputs / historical snapshots that MUST stay tracked.
reports/*
!reports/town_distinctness_calibration.json
!reports/cultivation_style_baseline_hashes.txt

